{
  "number": 710,
  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/pull/710",
  "title": "style(require/from): Never use .js in requires and froms",
  "body": "For `require`s\n\n``` sh\nag -l \"require\\(.*.js.\\)\" | xargs -I {} sed -i -r '/(hogan|instantsearch)/! s#(require\\(.*)\\.js(.\\))#\\1\\2#g' {}\n```\n\nFor `import ... from ...`\n\n``` sh\nag -l \"import .* from .*\\.js\" | xargs -I {} sed -i -r 's/(import.*from .*)\\.js/\\1/g' {}\n```\n\nJust here for consistency.\n",
